<h2>Hex Keypad</h2>
<p>
Default 2 hex keypads is configured. The second keypad is configured by selecting checkbox 'VP580 Expansion Keypad' (highlighted in orange) or checkbox 'VP590 Colour Board' (highlighted in yellow). The only known game using 2 keypads is the Chip-8X game blockout.
</p>
<p>
To change and view the hex keypad to PC key mapping select the 'Key Map' button (highlighted in green), see also section <a href="KeyMappingMain.htm">Key Mapping</a>
</p>
<h2>Keyboard</h2>
<p>
To use the VIP with ASCII keyboard support select the keyboard checkbox (highlighted in blue). 
</p>
